……。"},{"id":1252945,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1252945","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"ソレすなわち、私たちは同志、ということ","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2023-10-25","comment":21,"desc":"アキツを殺してしまったことで塞ぎこんでいたゴローは、ホノカからどんな悩みでも解決してくれる“天使くん”の話を聞く。「天使くんの謎を暴きたい」と言う科学研究会のチカに付きまとわれながら、学校にいる天使くんを探すゴロー。２人はチカの調べた情報を元に天使くん・タツヤを見つけるが、彼はヤンキーのような風貌のコウキに絡まれていて……。"},{"id":1252946,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1252946","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2023-11-01","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1252947,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1252947","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2023-11-08","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1252948,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1252948","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2023-11-15","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1252949,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1252949","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2023-11-22","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1252950,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1252950","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2023-11-29","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1252951,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1252951","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2023-12-06","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1252952,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1252952","type":0,"sort":11,"name":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2023-12-13","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1252953,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1252953","type":0,"sort":12,"name":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2023-12-20","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1255908,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1255908","type":0,"sort":13,"name":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2023-12-27","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1255909,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1255909","type":0,"sort":14,"name":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2024-01-03","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1255910,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1255910","type":0,"sort":15,"name":"","duration":"00:22:50","airdate":"2024-01-10","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1255911,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1255911","type":0,"sort":16,"name":"","duration":"0